WEBVTT

00:02.681 --> 00:06.286
So Owen can eat pretty much anything
he wants at this point, right?

00:06.310 --> 00:07.579
Except peanut butter.

00:07.603 --> 00:09.622
He gets little hives when
he eats peanut butter.

00:09.646 --> 00:11.615
Ross, you know, he sort
of feeds himself now.

00:11.648 --> 00:13.710
No kidding? That's amazing.

00:13.734 --> 00:14.669
Not really.

00:14.693 --> 00:17.422
I mean, he's 16 months. It'd
be kind of scary if he didn't.

00:17.446 --> 00:21.625
See, I, I didn't know that, and this thing
he's doing, for example, right now,

00:21.992 --> 00:24.794
squinching up his face and holding
his breath, what does that mean?

00:26.121 --> 00:27.724
- Bless you.
- God bless you.

00:27.748 --> 00:29.257
He's playing a game, right?

00:29.416 --> 00:30.717
No, he's pooping.

00:33.086 --> 00:34.262
Oh.

00:35.797 --> 00:36.858
Oh, right.

00:36.882 --> 00:40.060
I'll change him. I can't
smell anything, anyway.

00:40.427 --> 00:42.145
How do you know what
kind of diapers to use?

00:42.554 --> 00:44.981
I mean, do you buy them all, and
then kind of let him decide?

00:50.103 --> 00:51.821
Okay, um,

00:52.773 --> 00:55.585
about a year and a half ago,
I put my name on this list,

00:55.609 --> 00:58.463
and I filled out some forms and
I went in for an interview

00:58.487 --> 01:01.998
and I didn't say anything about it because I
really didn't believe anything would happen.

01:02.324 --> 01:04.876
I mean, at least, not
for a really long time.

01:05.953 --> 01:08.640
I mean, you know, being
a single guy, and...

01:08.664 --> 01:11.466
But I've wanted this
for a long time,

01:11.625 --> 01:16.471
so anyway, about 36 hours
ago, this baby girl was born,

01:18.298 --> 01:22.519
and, amazingly, yesterday
the agency called.

01:24.304 --> 01:26.856
So that's why diapers kind
of matter to me right now.

01:27.057 --> 01:28.326
Wow!

01:28.350 --> 01:29.494
Ross.

01:29.518 --> 01:31.111
Ross!

01:31.228 --> 01:32.529
That's great!

01:33.397 --> 01:34.499
It's so exciting.

01:34.523 --> 01:36.282
Oh, it's great.

01:39.903 --> 01:41.162
Something going on?

01:41.405 --> 01:43.623
You'll never guess
who's having a baby.

01:49.454 --> 01:51.849
The thing is, we were
always so careful.

01:51.873 --> 01:54.185
I mean, we have never
not been careful.

01:54.209 --> 01:55.552
Not once, right?

01:55.585 --> 01:58.398
Twenty five, 24, 23...

01:58.422 --> 02:01.192
And you always use a
real, established brand,

02:01.216 --> 02:04.185
not, like, "Jerry's Condoms"
or anything, right?

02:04.428 --> 02:06.698
Seventeen, 16, 15...

02:06.722 --> 02:09.441
So there's no way.

02:09.975 --> 02:11.735
I mean, there's no way, right?

02:12.019 --> 02:15.613
Right. None. Zero. Zip.

02:19.276 --> 02:22.203
I know I'm pregnant.
I just know it.

02:24.698 --> 02:25.957
Oh, God.

02:31.038 --> 02:33.558
Look, I just want you to know...

02:33.582 --> 02:34.966
Uh-huh.

02:35.792 --> 02:38.053
- Whatever happens...
- Mmm-hmm.

02:38.420 --> 02:41.348
I am never, ever
having sex again.

02:42.007 --> 02:43.350
Mmm-hmm.

